---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Home" description="Sydney-based technology leader, author, and community builder.">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Nikhil Kulkarni</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Sydney-based technology leader, author, and community builder.</p>
      <p class="sub">AI product practitioner. Published commentator. Active voice at the Australia–India intersection.</p>
      <a href="/about" class="cta">About me &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo">
      <img src="/images/author-pic.jpg" alt="Nikhil Kulkarni" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pillars">
    <a href="/ai-product" class="pillar-card card-ai">
      <div class="card-image">
        <img src="/images/atlassian-speaking.jpg" alt="Nikhil speaking at Atlassian" />
      </div>
      <h2>AI &amp; Product Leadership</h2>
      <p>Founding PM lead for Rovo, Atlassian's AI product. 20+ years across ecommerce, B2B SaaS, and startups.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/australia-india" class="pillar-card card-india">
      <div class="card-image">
        <img src="/images/new-india-house.jpg" alt="Nikhil speaking at New India House, SXSW Sydney" />
      </div>
      <h2>Australia–India</h2>
      <p>AIBC NSW Committee. Australia India Youth Dialogue. New India House at SXSW Sydney 2025. LBW Trust Ambassador.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/writing" class="pillar-card card-writing">
      <div class="card-image">
        <img src="/images/writing-smh.jpg" alt="Nikhil Kulkarni opinion piece in the Sydney Morning Herald" />
      </div>
      <h2>Writing &amp; Commentary</h2>
      <p>Opinion pieces in the Sydney Morning Herald, Australian Financial Review, and Canberra Times. 170+ blog posts.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/book" class="pillar-card card-book">
      <div class="card-image">
        <img src="/images/book-tv.jpg" alt="Nikhil Kulkarni on Channel 9 Today Extra, Author of My Summer of Cricket" />
      </div>
      <h2>Book</h2>
      <p><em>My Summer of Cricket</em> — on cricket, migration, identity, and belonging. Featured on Channel 9's Today.</p>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="now">
    <p>
      Currently independent — following 7.5 years at Atlassian. Open to advisory, speaking, and strategic conversations.
      <a href="/contact">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
    </p>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 260px;
    height: 260px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  /* Photo strip cards — remove default padding, re-apply inside */
  .card-ai,
  .card-india,
  .card-book,
  .card-writing {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .card-ai h2, .card-ai p,
  .card-india h2, .card-india p,
  .card-book h2, .card-book p,
  .card-writing h2, .card-writing p {
    padding: 0 1.75rem;
  }

  .card-ai h2, .card-india h2,
  .card-book h2, .card-writing h2 {
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .card-ai p, .card-india p,
  .card-book p, .card-writing p {
    padding-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .card-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 160px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 7px 7px 0 0;
  }

  .card-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
  }

  /* Coloured borders per pillar */
  .card-ai      { border-color: #2563eb; }
  .card-india   { border-color: #f59e0b; }
  .card-writing { border-color: #16a34a; }
  .card-book    { border-color: #dc2626; }

  /* Zoom in on the Australia-India card */
  .card-india .card-image img {
    transform: scale(1.3);
    transform-origin: center center;
  }

  /* Shift book card left so the name lower-third is visible */
  .card-book .card-image img {
    object-position: left center;
  }

  .pillar-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .pillar-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .now {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .now a {
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-photo img {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
    }
  }
</style>
